Title: Work Order: Operation: Shieldwall I
Description:
<Yoon's writing decorates the page though his feelings seem conflicted.>

I normally try to stay out of conflict, but an order is an order. Since you are of the Alliance I decided to pass this order your way.

Operation: Shieldwall has requested a whole heap of witchberries.

I can't be sure, but I think they have an idea to use them in some sort of weapon.
ObjectivesText: Plant 8 Witchberry Seeds on Sunsong Ranch.
